        <li><strong>Recital pride:</strong> "The recital was the best thing that happened to our family this year. She practiced for weeks and it showed."</li>
        <li><strong>Long-term commitment:</strong> "Three years in and we have zero plans to stop. Best investment we've made for our kids."</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">When to ask for a testimonial</h2>
      <p>Ask after a student reaches a milestone — their first song, first performance, or first year of lessons. Send your SocialProof collection link via text or email immediately after a great lesson while the emotion is fresh. Display testimonials on your website's booking page and Google Business Profile link for maximum enrollment impact.</p>

